| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-2122 — Recovery Inhibition (ransomhub)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 7979f3d4-8751-5384-abfe-a5d4a8a2ad3e"
